<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ALO Organization - Projects</title>

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/simplelightbox/2.14.3/simple-lightbox.min.css">

    <style>
        /* Custom scrollbar for better look */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #f1f1f1; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #15803d; border-radius: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50 font-sans">

    <div class="bg-green-900 text-white text-sm">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center px-4 py-2 gap-2">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 hidden md:flex">
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot mr-1"></i> Naogaon, Bangladesh</span>
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-phone mr-1"></i> +8801712987908</span>
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope mr-1"></i> alo.bd433@gmail.com</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-lg">
                <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook cursor-pointer hover:text-orange-400 transition"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-youtube cursor-pointer hover:text-orange-400 transition"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram cursor-pointer hover:text-orange-400 transition"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <nav class="bg-white shadow-md sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10  rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold"> <img src="/ALO_LOGO_PNG.png" class="h-10"></div>
                    <span class="font-semibold  md:block">ALO Organization</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="hidden md:flex gap-8 font-medium items-center">
                    <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-green-700 transition">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-green-700 transition">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="text-green-700 font-bold border-b-2 border-green-700">Projects</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-green-700 transition">Contact</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="bg-orange-500 text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-orange-600 transition shadow-md">Donate Now</a></li>
                </ul>
                <button id="menuBtn" class="md:hidden text-2xl text-green-900"><i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div id="mobileMenu" class="hidden md:hidden pb-6 space-y-4 animate-fade-in">
                <a href="/" class="block font-medium hover:text-green-700">Home</a>
                <a href="#" class="block font-medium hover:text-green-700">About</a>
                <a href="#" class="block font-medium text-green-700">Projects</a>
                <a href="#" class="block font-medium hover:text-green-700">Contact</a>
                <a href="#" class="block bg-orange-500 text-white text-center py-2 rounded">Donate Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- ================= HERO ================= -->
<section
class="relative bg-[url('/IMG_2632.JPG.jpeg')] bg-cover bg-center h-[55vh] flex items-center">

<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>

<div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-white">
  <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
    Together We Can Build a Just &<br>
     Equal Society
  </h1>

  <p class="max-w-xl mb-6">
    ALO is a rights-based development organization committed to empowering marginalized and indigenous communities to create a peaceful and inclusive society—free from discrimination and poverty—where everyone enjoys equal access to justice and opportunities. 
  </p>

  <div class="flex gap-4">
    <a class="bg-green-700 px-6 py-3 rounded">Our Projects</a>
    <a class="bg-orange-500 px-6 py-3 rounded">Donate Now</a>
  </div>
</div>

</section>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-6xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-800">Our Impactful Projects</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">Empowering communities through sustainable development</p>
            <div class="w-24 h-1.5 bg-green-600 mx-auto mt-4 rounded-full"></div>
        </div>

        <% if(projects && projects.length > 0) { %>
            <% projects.forEach(project => { %>
                
                <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 mb-16 transition-all hover:shadow-2xl">
                    
                    <div class="relative h-64 md:h-[450px] overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="/uploads/<%= project.coverimage %>" alt="<%= project.projectTitle %>" class="w-full  object-cover center transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105  object-cover space-y-4">

                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 to-transparent w-full p-6">
                            <span class="bg-orange-500 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 inline-block">
                                <%= project.projectTitle %>
                            </span>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white"><%= project.projectname  %></h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="p-6 md:p-12">
                        <div class="max-w-4xl">
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-8">
                                <%= project.description %>
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 border-y border-gray-100 py-8 mb-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-700 text-xl">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase">Project Area</span>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800"><%= project.projectarea %></p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600 text-xl">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase">Beneficiaries</span>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800"><%= project.beneficiary %></p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 text-xl">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase">Primary Goal</span>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800"><%= project.projectgoal %></p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <% if(project.projectobjectives && project.projectobjectives.length > 0) { %>
                        <div class="mb-10">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800 flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-8 h-1 bg-green-600"></span> Key Objectives
                            </h4>
                            <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                                <% project.projectobjectives.forEach(obj => { %>
                                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-green-500">
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-green-600"></i>
                                        <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"><%= obj %></span>
                                    </li>
                                <% }) %>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>

                        <% if(project.extraimage && project.extraimage.length > 0) { %>
                        <div class="mt-12">
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest italic text-center">Visual Highlights</h4>
                            <div class="project-gallery grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                                <% project.extraimage.forEach(img => { %>
                                    <a href="/uploads/<%= img %>" class="group relative h-40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-md border-2 border-transparent hover:border-green-500 transition-all">
                                        <img src="/uploads/<%= img %>" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-110" alt="Gallery Image">
                                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity flex items-center justify-center">
                                            <i class="fa-solid fa-expand text-white text-2xl"></i>
                                        </div>
                                    </a>
                                <% }) %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>

                    </div>
                </div>

            <% }) %>
        <% } else { %>
            <div class="text-center py-20 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-dashed border-gray-300">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-folder-open text-gray-300 text-6xl mb-4"></i>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-xl font-medium">No projects available at this moment.</p>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white text-center py-10 mt-10">
        <div class="mb-6 flex justify-center gap-6 text-2xl">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook hover:text-orange-500 cursor-pointer"></i>
            <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter hover:text-orange-500 cursor-pointer"></i>
            <i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin hover:text-orange-500 cursor-pointer"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">© 2026 ALO Organization — Building a Just & Equal Society</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/simplelightbox/2.14.3/simple-lightbox.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Mobile Menu Toggle
        const btn = document.getElementById("menuBtn");
        const menu = document.getElementById("mobileMenu");
        btn.addEventListener("click", () => menu.classList.toggle("hidden"));

        // Initialize Lightbox for all project galleries
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            var lightbox = new SimpleLightbox('.project-gallery a', {
                overlayOpacity: 0.9,
                showCounter: true,
                uniqueImages: true,
                fadeSpeed: 300
            });
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>



ALO Technology Hub
Climate Adaptive Agriculture Technology Hub
Empowering farmers with innovative and climate-resilient agricultural solutions.

About the ALO Technology Hub
ALO Climate Adaptive Agriculture Technology Hub is an innovative center dedicated to climate-resilient agricultural hub practices. Located in Naogaon, Bangladesh, it empowers farmers with hands-on demonstrations of sustainable farming technologies to combat climate change.
✔ Climate-Smart Practices
✔ Hands-On Demonstrations
✔ Sustainable Development
✔ Indigenous Knowledge Goals (UBs)
Key Features of the Hub
Solar Water Pumps
Solar irrigation for efficient water management
Vertical Hydroponics
Space-saving soilless farming method
Vermicomposting Units
Organic waste to produce nutrient-rich compost
Organic Seed Banks
Indigenous, climate-resilient seed preservation


Our Facilities
Hands-On Training
Our hub offers comprehensive facilities to support sustainable agriculture initiatives.
Demonstration Plots
Farmers receive hands-on training, demonstrations, and access to innovative agricultural technologies.
